---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>⚙️ Backend Brain. 🎮 Gamer at Heart.</h1>
			<p>
				Hey, I’m a Senior Backend Developer with 7.5+ years of building systems that don’t just work —
				they scale, survive traffic spikes, and refuse to crash under pressure.
			</p>

			<p>
				I specialize in designing distributed systems, event-driven architectures, and backend systems
				that handle real-world chaos using tools like Kafka, Redis, Node.js, and AWS.
				My goal? Transition into a Backend Architect role and build systems that outlive trends.
			</p>

			<p>
				But that’s not all.
			</p>

			<p>
				I’m currently building a bootstrap esports-tech platform designed to make esports
				more accessible in India — empowering gamers to earn,
				compete, and grow without depending on broken systems.
				Think kirana-shop economics, but for esports.
			</p>

			<p>
				When I’m not designing APIs or optimizing performance,
				I’m creating gaming content 🎮 and chasing my goal of being a big streamer —
				one stream, one short, one improvement at a time.
			</p>

			<h3>🚀 What I’m Building</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>⚡ Scalable backend systems with clean architecture</li>
				<li>📡 Event-driven services using Kafka</li>
				<li>🏏 An esports platform to help gamers monetize their passion</li>
				<li>🧠 Constantly leveling up system design & architecture skills</li>
				<li>🎮 Gaming content with storytelling & strategy</li>
			</ul>

			<h3>💡 What I Believe</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Systems should be simple to understand but hard to break</li>
				<li>Good architecture is invisible when done right</li>
				<li>Sports/Gaming can change lives if monetized correctly</li>
				<li>Consistency beats motivation</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				If you're into backend engineering, scalable systems,
				sports-tech innovation, or gaming culture —
				you’ll probably enjoy what I’m building.
			</p>

			<p>
				Welcome to my digital playground.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer/>
	</body>
</html>
